                    </button>
                    <button class="menu-button" onclick="executeFunction('fixPhoneNumbers')">
                        <span class="icon">üìû</span>
                        <span class="text">‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏Ç‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÇ‡∏ó‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏°‡∏µ 0 ‡∏ô‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤</span>
