                    </button>
                    <button class="menu-button" onclick="executeFunction('clearPairingData')">
                        <span class="icon">üóëÔ∏è</span>
                        <span class="text">Clear Pairing (‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏£‡πå‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏à‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏π‡πà‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î)</span>
